 Iron Maiden 的 Nicko McBain 将“从繁琐的巡演生活方式中退一步” https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-nicko-mcbain-to-take-a-step-back-from-the-grind-of-the-extective-touring-lifestyle-3820013？你tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=iron-maidens-nicko-mcbain 从广泛的巡演生活方式的磨难中退一步Max PilleySat, 07 Dec 2024 17:05:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3820013 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们周六（12 月 7 日）在圣保罗的演出将是 McBrain 与乐队的最后一场演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-nicko-mcbain-to-take-a-step-back-from-the-grind-of-the-extensive-touring-lifestyle-3820013">《铁娘子》乐队成员尼科·麦克贝恩 (Nicko McBain) 的“从繁重的巡演生活方式的苦差事中退一步”的</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/nicko_mcbrain_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a>鼓手 Nicko McBrain 宣布他将退出乐队现场演奏。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="748" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/iron-maiden-senjutsu-review-3035836"><b>Iron Maiden – “Senjutsu”评论：富有想象力的即时经典</b></a></li></ul><p>这位打击乐手于 1982 年加入这支传奇金属乐队，取代了克莱夫·伯尔 (Clive Burr)，并在自 1983 年的《Piece Of Mind》以来的所有专辑中演奏。然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-drummer-nicko-mcbrain-reveals-he-suffered-stroke-that-left-him-paralysed-on-one-side-3477778">2023 年 1 月，他确实遭遇了轻微中风，即短暂性脑缺血发作，</a>导致他右侧从肩膀以下部分瘫痪。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-announce-2024-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3524133">随着他们的“The Future Past”世界巡演接近尾声</a>，McBrain 确认周六（12 月 7 日）在圣保罗的演出将是他与乐队的最后一次演出。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">铁娘子的公告<a href="https://t.co/MzFfb8DC4A">pic.twitter.com/MzFfb8DC4A</a></p><p> — 铁娘子 (@IronMaiden) <a href="https://twitter.com/IronMaiden/status/1865380784678297763?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 7 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他在社交媒体上发帖称：“经过深思熟虑，我怀着悲喜交加的心情，宣布决定从繁重的巡演生活方式中退一步。” “我祝愿乐队前进取得成功。”</p><p> “然而，我将继续坚定地成为 Iron Maiden 家族的一员，致力于各种项目，”他继续说道。他补充说，他将继续参与他的企业 The Britain Drum Company、Nicko McBrain&#39;s Drum One、Titanium Tart 和 Rock-N-Roll Ribs。</p><p> “我能说什么？过去 42 年与 Maiden 一起巡演是一次令人难以置信的旅程！对于我忠实的粉丝群，你们让这一切都是值得的，我爱你们！感谢我忠诚的妻子丽贝卡，你让一切变得更加轻松，我爱你！我的孩子贾斯汀和尼古拉斯，感谢你们对缺席的理解，我爱你们！对于一直在我身边的朋友们，我爱你们！对于我的乐队成员来说，你们让梦想成真，我爱你们！”</p><p> “展望未来，我充满兴奋和希望！”他总结道。 “我很快就会见到你们，愿上帝保佑你们所有人，当然还有《Up the Irons!》” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDRy0xmCn8O/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.8