charli-xcx-to-headline-and-curate-own-party-girl-festival-at-londons-lido-2025-buy-tickets-3815487">在伦敦 LIDO 音乐节上策划一天的演出，届时她将带来一场超值表演</a>。</p><p>此外，她还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-huge-summer-2025-shows-in-belfast-and-dublin-3814479">在贝尔法斯特和都柏林举办两场户外演出</a>，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">2025 年 Coachella</a>音乐节上表演，并在巴塞罗那和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">波尔图</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-she-chappell-roan-and-sabrina-carpenter-headlining-primavera-sound-2025-is-the-holy-trinity-3806307">Primavera Sound 上表演</a>。除此之外，她还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-us-brat-arena-tour-2025-buy-tickets-3815161">将于四月和五月进行美国舞台巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-gillian-anderson-exchange-over-being-chic-and-cunty-3820009">Charli XCX 和 Gillian Anderson 就“时髦又性感”交换意见的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
